        <name>Kaiseregg</name>
        <desc>A stunning view over the Bernese Alps and Fribourg Pre-Alps awaits you at the summit of the Kaiseregg. This demanding hike is one of the classics for mountain lovers in the canton of Fribourg.</desc>
